493
00:28:23,740 --> 00:28:26,140
Lawyer Kim says our Se Ri was switched
with someone else.

494
00:28:26,140 --> 00:28:27,180
Manager Gong, did you know about this?

495
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:29,980
If you could just make sure Ms. Kyung Chae
never finds out about this,

496
00:28:30,010 --> 00:28:31,750
I would be forever in your debt.

497
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:34,280
He'll try to get rid of me first
since I'm the biggest thorn in their side.

498
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:36,920
I told you to get rid of
that jerk Moon Tae Kyung today!

499
00:28:37,020 --> 00:28:38,490
Tae Kyung is in danger!

500
00:28:38,490 --> 00:28:40,860
